&lt;text x="42" y="50" font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif" font-size="24" font-weight="800" fill="#0f172a"&gt;Graph Optimization: request path&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;g font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif"&gt;
