&lt;h2&gt;The takeaway&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="the-takeaway"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#the-takeaway" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Graph optimization converts a correct model into a hardware plan. The gain comes from global visibility, but so does the responsibility to validate shapes, precision, and portability.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>